    <briefdescription>
<para>Visual style parameters for IMGUI widgets. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Set via <ref refid="syn__imgui_8c_1a0425e085ef0132cb190e6275b7d4c8b1" kindref="member">syn_imgui_set_style()</ref>. <ref refid="syn__imgui_8c_1a5ddf2780b1ce1b1ceaa85ae34fa48352" kindref="member">syn_imgui_init()</ref> loads the defaults (monochrome-friendly: white-on-black, matching the existing hardcoded colors) so existing code is unaffected. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
